title: Authorizes the county of Westchester to issue serial bonds to finance certain payments over a period of five years
summary: Authorizes the county of Westchester to issue serial bonds to finance certain payments over a period of five years for any costs associated with or related to the 2010 Early Retirement Incentive.
actClause: AN ACT to authorize the county of Westchester to issue serial bonds to finance certain payments over a period of five years
